{"tid":1052427,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DC9疑出蠱惑 摺錢找少100蚊 乘客險被騙","createTime":"2019-03-08T09:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T16:37:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a602ae3771321ee6572c85aec40a6ea4e4424009","tid":1052427,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T09:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kHQNlDqtWsRdskx4Z0RC2g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/bbfc9869bc520745b1014f0ae3b0c653\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FkHQNlDqtWsRdskx4Z0RC2g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2Fbbfc9869bc520745b1014f0ae3b0c653&h=cb331de2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有心還是故意？近日有網民指的士司機找錢時，將2張100元紙幣摺起，當作300元找贖，幸好她發現及時。事件更引來不少網民分享類似經歷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事主在Facebook群組「將軍澳」發文，指星期二（5日）晚上乘搭的士，車費為192元。她當時付了一張500元。惟司機找贖時，疑將2張100元紙幣摺起，驟眼看有如3張，但司機實際只找回208元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她指自己幸好有看清楚，當場「叫司機畀番100蚊我」。她又呼籲其他乘客︰「要數清楚先落車」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛表示曾有類似遭遇︰「畀咗張1000蚊司機，司機明知都當100找，落車即刻踩油走」、「試過搭120元，畀200元，佢以為唔使找當畀貼士」、「夜晚將車內支燈熄咗，博你畀錯錢」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E7%96%91%E5%87%BA%E8%A0%B1%E6%83%91-%E6%91%BA%E9%8C%A2%E6%89%BE%E5%B0%91100%E8%9A%8A-%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%AE%A2%E9%9A%AA%E8%A2%AB%E9%A8%99-083251620.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A0%25B1%25E6%2583%2591-%25E6%2591%25BA%25E9%258C%25A2%25E6%2589%25BE%25E5%25B0%2591100%25E8%259A%258A-%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E9%259A%25AA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%25A8%2599-083251620.html&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMlDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=4c9a7715\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E7%96%91%E5